<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="long-adj">long <strong><em>adj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /lɒŋ/    美 /lɔːŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(距离、长度) 长的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>six feet long 
6英尺长</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a long journey / flight / drive
长途旅行/飞行/驾驶</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>长时间的；长期的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We would be separated <strong>for a long time</strong>. 
我们将会分开很长一段时间。</p><footer> 2010 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All our hard work will be worth it <strong>in the long run</strong>.
从长远来看，我们的辛苦都是值得的。</p></div></div>